# Code Owners for GHAS Workshop Repository
# Used to demonstrate security governance concepts in Phase 5

# Default owners for everything in the repo
* @security-team

# Security-sensitive files require security team review
/.github/workflows/ @security-team
/.github/dependabot.yml @security-team
/SECURITY.md @security-team

# Application code owners
/python-api/ @backend-team @security-team
/node-frontend/ @frontend-team @security-team
/java-backend/ @backend-team @security-team

# Documentation
/docs/ @documentation-team
/README.md @documentation-team

# Configuration files
*.yml @devops-team
*.yaml @devops-team
*.json @devops-team
